title: Ep. #15 | Catching Up: pH-1
description:
In this week’s episode of @daebakshow, we have the amazing pH-1 joining us. From coding full time to becoming one of the hottest artists in Korea, pH-1’s journey is like no other. Make sure to follow us on all our socials @daebakshow and at www.daebakshow.com We hope you enjoy! #ph1 #halo #malibu #daebakshow #ericnam
